		<p>"Okay. Well I know I haven't been around that much lately, and you're under no obligation to sit here and listen to all of this, but...you're the only person I can think of who might understand."</p>
		<p>Joey swallowed nervously; she hadn't realized how hard this would be to talk about.</p>
